---
source: tests/cli.rs
expression: "help_output(& [\"version\", \"--help\"])"
---
Print the hpds version

The same value as `hpds --version`, provided as a subcommand for scripts.

Usage: hpds version [OPTIONS]

Options:
  -v, --verbose
          Show more detail (underlying commands, tool names)

  -q, --quiet
          Suppress all output except errors

      --no-color
          Disable colored output

      --config <PATH>
          Use this config file instead of discovering hpds.toml

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')
